<h3>Cocktails — Overview</h3>
<p>The Cocktails module lets your members browse, rate and submit cocktail recipes.</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Recipes</strong> hold a name, summary, method, glass, difficulty, prep time, servings and a photo.</li>
    <li><strong>Ingredients</strong> are an admin-curated master list; each recipe references them as measured lines (amount + unit).</li>
    <li><strong>Categories, Glasses and Tags</strong> organise and help users discover recipes.</li>
    <li><strong>Ratings</strong> (1–5 stars, one per user) and <strong>Favorites</strong> drive the "Top rated" lists and the user's personal collection.</li>
</ul>
<p>Configure editors, moderation, guest rating, image sizes and pager sizes under <em>Preferences</em>. Set who may submit, auto-approve, edit own recipes and rate under <em>Permissions</em>.</p>
